title: 201: NFC Preview
itunes:title: 201: NFC Preview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks get you ready for the 2017 season by diving into the NFC team by team. The guys also bring on former LA Rams coach John Lilly for the first time this season to give a coach's perspective on the NFC South and share quite the story from Bucky's past.
